Name: iggytools
Version: 0.1
Summary: Genome and database downloader
Home-page: http://github.com/harvardinformatics/iggytools
Author: Chris Williams
Author-email: wilcliams@gmail.com
License: GPLv3
Description: Iggyref downloads genomes and databases from EBI, Ensembl, NCBI and other sources. 
        Some postprocessing is performed, such as decompression, format coversion and the 
        generation of bowtie2 indexes for fasta files. 
        
